<doc id="296408" wikidata="Q7390205" url="?curid=296408" title="SHIK">
<text>The National Informative Service (), commonly known as SHIK, was an intelligence service agency created in 1991 by the Albanian People&#x27;s Assembly. It was the successor to Sigurimi, the notorious secret service agency which repressed anti-communist dissent during the communist government of 1944–1991. The agency was succeeded by SHISH in 1997.

== Directors ==
